To allow SVG upload, simply add this code to your themeâ€™s functions.php file:

PHP

function cc_mime_types($mimes) {
  $mimes['svg'] = 'image/svg+xml';
  return $mimes;
}
add_filter('upload_mimes', 'cc_mime_types');




You can add this your CSS

.svg-image {
  max-width:100%;
  height:auto;
  width:auto;
}
